@PaymentOrchestratorLiteApi_HostAddress = https://localhost:5000

### BEFORE RUNNING, MAKE SURE THE API IS RUNNING:
### Locally - https://localhost:5000
### Docker - http://localhost:5000

### Create Payment
POST {{PaymentOrchestratorLiteApi_HostAddress}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CUST001",
  "amount": 99.99
}

### Create Another Payment
POST {{PaymentOrchestratorLiteApi_HostAddress}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CUST002",
  "amount": 250.00
}

### Get All Payments
GET {{PaymentOrchestratorLiteApi_HostAddress}}/payments
Accept: application/json

### Confirm Payment (replace with actual payment ID)
POST {{PaymentOrchestratorLiteApi_HostAddress}}/simulate-confirmation/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

